{"type": "article", "id": 14600, "title": "新版“方形系统”", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-08T06:59:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000312pTvZXLqHNblf7jRK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t巴黎家装博览会和家具品牌 karakter 合作，重新推出了意大利设计师约•科伦博( Joe Colombo )在1969年的设计产品“ square system（方形系统）”。使用铝合金材质以替代原版的塑料，增加了组合的丰富度，也增强了这套设计的价值。这套产品延续了模块化的结构，可以灵活组合成任何功能的桌子或者书架，是当代设计中的经典。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142054UoEC7FJqu8bMsr34.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"584\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072614205597A05cjGdOyzFZer.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"648\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79217604\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142055Hh2d1tT4paPb5zIx.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"568\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69437653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}